title: Police: Man found shot to death on Long Island
text:
NEW CASSEL, N.Y. (AP) - Police say a man was fatally shot near a Long Island business.
Nassau County police responded to reports of shots fired in New Cassel on Monday night. Police found a 31-year-old man near Prospect Avenue with multiple gunshot wounds.
He was taken to Nassau University Medical Center in East Meadow where he later died.
Police have not determined a motive for the shooting. No arrests were made as of Monday night.
